name: DIVERSION | Interjet A320-214(SL) [XA-CRM] Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport
description:
On December 7th, the day of Air Canada's 737MAX touch and goes, Calgary also received a diversion from Vancouver earlier that morning in the form of this Interjet A320, operating Mexico City to Vancouver when it diverted here around 0630 local time. They ended up waiting 2 hours for fuel as there was nobody available to service them. Still nice to see this Mexican carrier here! Here's XA-CRM departing at the break of dawn for Vancouver, with some incredible sunrise lighting! ATC is included, hope you enjoy my first catch of this airline!

Thanks for watching!
